<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title">Print Server</h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents">
<p class="para">Önnur algeng notkun á Samba er að stilla það til að deila prenturum, sem eru annaðhvort beintengdir eða á staðarnetinu, með Ubuntu netþjóni. Líkt og með <a class="xref" href="samba-fileserver.html" title="File Server">File Server</a> þá mun þessi hluti stilla Samba til að leyfa öllum útstöðvum að nota uppsetta prentara án þess að biðja um notendanafn eða lykilorð.</p>
<p class="para">Fyrir öruggari uppsetningu skoðið <a class="xref" href="samba-fileprint-security.html" title="Securing File and Print Server">Securing File and Print Server</a>.</p>
</div>
<div class="links sectionlinks" role="navigation"><ul>
<li class="links"><a class="xref" href="samba-printserver.html#samba-printserver-installation" title="Uppsetning">Uppsetning</a></li>
<li class="links"><a class="xref" href="samba-printserver.html#samba-printserver-configuration" title="Stilling">Stilling</a></li>
<li class="links"><a class="xref" href="samba-printserver.html#samba-printserver-resources" title="Tilföng">Tilföng</a></li>
</ul></div>
<div class="sect2 sect" id="samba-printserver-installation"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">Uppsetning</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="para">Áður en farið er í uppsetningu og stillingu á Samba þá er best að hafa grunnþekkingu uppsetningu á <span class="app application">CUPS</span>. Skoðið <a class="xref" href="cups.html" title="CUPS - Print Server">CUPS - Print Server</a> fyrir ýtarlegri upplýsingar.</p>
<p class="para">Til að setja upp <span class="app application">samba</span>  pakkann, sláið eftirfarandi inn í útstöðvarglugga.</p>
<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">sudo apt install samba</span>
</pre></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
<div class="sect2 sect" id="samba-printserver-configuration"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">Stilling</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="para">
    After installing samba edit <span class="file filename">/etc/samba/smb.conf</span>.  Change the <span class="em emphasis">workgroup</span> 
    attribute to what is appropriate for your network, and change <span class="em emphasis">security</span> to 
    <span class="em emphasis">user</span>:
    </p>
<div class="code"><pre class="contents ">   workgroup = EXAMPLE
   ...
   security = user
</pre></div>
<p class="para">Í <span class="em emphasis">[printers]</span> hlutanum breyttu þá <span class="em emphasis">guest ok</span> valkostinum í <span class="em emphasis">yes</span>:</p>
<div class="code"><pre class="contents ">   browsable = yes
   guest ok = yes
</pre></div>
<p class="para">Eftir að hafa breytt <span class="file filename">smb.conf</span> endurræsið þá Samba:</p>
<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">sudo systemctl restart smbd.service nmbd.service</span>
</pre></div>
<p class="para">Sjálfgefinn Samba uppsetning mun deila öllum uppsettum prenturum sjálfkrafa. Einfaldlega setjið viðkomandi prentara upp á viðkomandi Windows útstöð.</p>
</div></div>
</div></div>
<div class="sect2 sect" id="samba-printserver-resources"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">Tilföng</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents"><div class="list itemizedlist"><ul class="list itemizedlist">
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para">Fyrir ýtarlegri Samba uppsetningar skoðið þá <a href="http://samba.org/samba/docs/man/Samba-HOWTO-Collection/" class="ulink" title="http://samba.org/samba/docs/man/Samba-HOWTO-Collection/">Samba HOWTO Safnið</a></p>
        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para">Leiðbeiningarnar eru einnig fáanlegar hér <a href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/tg/detail/-/0131882228" class="ulink" title="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/tg/detail/-/0131882228">í prentformi</a>.</p>
        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para">O'Reilly's <a href="http://www.oreilly.com/catalog/9780596007690/" class="ulink" title="http://www.oreilly.com/catalog/9780596007690/">Using Samba</a> er annað gott tilvísunarrit.</p>
        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para">Skoðið einnig <a href="http://www.cups.org/" class="ulink" title="http://www.cups.org/">CUPS Heimasíðan</a> fyrir nánari upplýsingar og stillingar fyrir CUPS.</p>
        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
          <p class="para">
          The <a href="https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Samba" class="ulink" title="https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Samba">Ubuntu Wiki Samba </a> page.
          </p>
        </li>
</ul></div></div></div>
